text.tspan: Think about the beat of your travel this year. Did you log miles
touring on the road? Get A-list treatment at a VIP resort? Or
were you too busy planning new gigs to take a real vacation?
You don’t need the red carpet rolled out when you arrive (not
that you'd say no to one). But you're used to a luxurious life at
the top of the charts – and this year you indulged well.
